sentences.english: The northern or southern latitude beyond which trees do not grow.
sentences.chinese: 北緯或南緯線，超過該線，樹木不能生長。

sentences.english: The latitude of the ship is twenty degrees south.
sentences.chinese: 航船的緯度爲南緯二十度。

sentences.english: Farther south, they set later after sunset.
sentences.chinese: 在南緯地區，日落後晚些時候才降落。
